00:17:10,709 --> 00:17:12,629
as quickly and easily as possible.

336
00:17:13,797 --> 00:17:16,679
Perceptual uniqueness, though, can come in multiple forms.

337
00:17:16,679 --> 00:17:19,061
I wanted to take a second to highlight Caves of Qud

338
00:17:19,061 --> 00:17:22,303
as having an interesting approach to meaning.

