00:17:22,303 --> 00:17:25,606
Caves of Qud blurs the line between mechanical meaning

340
00:17:25,606 --> 00:17:28,468
and intrinsic writerly meaning here.

341
00:17:28,468 --> 00:17:31,250
You can see Mehmet is an individual

342
00:17:31,250 --> 00:17:32,871
