539
00:26:42,589 --> 00:26:47,711
an ancient Greek philosopher who specialized in writing about personality types and example

540
00:26:47,711 --> 00:26:50,253
activities that different personalities do.

541
00:26:50,253 --> 00:26:54,915
And feeding that in as a co-author will obviously have different effects than feeding in medieval

