575
00:28:16,869 --> 00:28:19,671
like they have no memory of their childhood

576
00:28:19,671 --> 00:28:22,052
or something equally unexpected.

577
00:28:22,052 --> 00:28:24,793
And that does take up some time in your planning,

578
00:28:24,793 --> 00:28:27,274
